---
title: Chili-Garlic Turkey Noodles with Peppers and Celery
description: Turkey and sambal-style sauce make a playful pair in this spicy noodle dish. Savoury vegetarian oyster sauce adds a Southeast Asian twist, while crowd-pleasing crispy shallots add a tasty crunch. These noodles will disappear in no time!
